name: Alpha Alpaca
description:
A herd of immortal alpacas is specially created from the Alpha planet which is far far far away... more than 99 trillion light-years from our galaxy. 9 of them have escaped from their boring earth to our sophisticated world. 

Tezy is the first one that arrives here. She is looking for a cozy home, a generous host family or a true best friend. She mentions, "Anyone who becomes my best friend; I will be beside him or her forever. Here you can see I stand by you here all day and night."
